#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:1
msgid "DeepSeek-V4-Pro"
msgstr "DeepSeek-V4-Pro"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:3
msgid "1 Introduction"
msgstr "1.简介"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:5
msgid "DeepSeek-V4 introduces several key upgrades over DeepSeek-V3:"
msgstr "DeepSeek-V4在DeepSeek-V3基础上引入了多项关键升级："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:7
msgid ""
"The Manifold-Constrained Hyper-Connections (mHC) to strengthen conventional "
"residual connections."
msgstr "流形约束超连接(mHC)增强传统残差连接。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:8
msgid ""
"A hybrid attention architecture, which greatly improves long-context "
"efficiency through Compress-4-Attention and Compress-128-Attention. For the "
"Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) components, it still adopts the DeepSeekMoE "
"architecture, with only minor adjustments."
msgstr ""
"混合注意力架构，通过Compress-4-Attention和Compress-128-Attention大幅提升长上下文效率。对于混合专家(MoE)组件，仍采用DeepSeekMoE架构，仅做少量调整。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:10
msgid ""
"DeepSeek-V4-Pro, the maximum reasoning effort mode of DeepSeek-V4, "
"significantly advances the knowledge capabilities of open-source models, "
"firmly establishing itself as the best open-source model available today. It"
" achieves top-tier performance in coding benchmarks and significantly "
"bridges the gap with leading closed-source models on reasoning and agentic "
"tasks."
msgstr ""
"DeepSeek-V4-Pro作为DeepSeek-V4的最大推理努力模式，显著提升了开源模型的知识能力，牢固确立了其作为当今最佳开源模型的地位。它在编码基准测试中达到顶级性能，并在推理和智能体任务上显著缩小了与领先闭源模型的差距。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:12
msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, including "
"supported features, feature configuration, environment preparation, single-"
"node and multi-node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档将展示该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点和多节点部署、精度及性能评估。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:14
msgid ""
"**Note**: Please replace the version placeholder above with your actual "
"validation version."
msgstr "**注意**：请将上述版本占位符替换为您实际的验证版本。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:16
msgid "2 Supported Features"
msgstr "2.支持特性"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:18
msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"参考[支持特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取模型的支持特性矩阵。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Pro.md:20
msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置。"

